Install on mac
brew install redis


•	Download latest redis version from http://download.redis.io/redis-stable.tar.gz.
•	Compile redis
Go to folder where you downloaded the redis
eg. cd / Applications/redis-4.0.2
make


•	After the compilation the src directory inside the Redis distribution is populated with the different executables that are part of Redis:
o	redis-server is the Redis Server itself.
o	redis-cli is the command line interface utility to talk with Redis.

•	Start redis server
            src/redis-server
•	Start redis client
            src/redis-client

